          <li><span><a href="javascript:history.back()">Back</a></span></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <section id='content'>
        <body>
          <h3>VoiceMail Assistant</h3>
          <h4>Instructions:</h4>
          <ol>
              <li>Choose an environment and login your RingCentral account.
                <div>You can setup a dedicated extension with a direct phone number and setup the voicemail inbox as discussed in <a href="#">this article.</a></div>
              </li>
              <li>Click the settings icon at the top-right corner and change the settings accordingly.</li>
              <li>Make a call to the phone number of the extension and leave a voicemail with question about how to call some API from RingCentral Developer platform.
                <div>Example messages</div>
                <div>"I have a problem to send SMS using RingCentral platorm. Please help."</div>
                <div>"I cannot login to the platform with my extension username and password. It looks like the server is down. Please call me back as soon as possible."</div>
              </li>
              <li>Wait to see the voicemail updated on the list</li>
          </ol>
        </body>
      </section>
      <%- include('_footer') %>
    </body>
